{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"I'm going to start here."},{"time":2000,"text":"This is a hand-lettered sign"},{"time":4000,"text":"that appeared in a mom and pop bakery"},{"time":6000,"text":"in my old neighborhood in Brooklyn a few years ago."},{"time":9000,"text":"The store owned one of those machines"},{"time":11000,"text":"that can print on plates of sugar."},{"time":13000,"text":"And kids could bring in drawings"},{"time":15000,"text":"and have the store print a sugar plate"},{"time":18000,"text":"for the top of their birthday cake."}]},{"cues":[{"time":20000,"text":"But unfortunately, one of the things kids liked to draw"},{"time":23000,"text":"was cartoon characters."},{"time":25000,"text":"They liked to draw the Little Mermaid,"},{"time":27000,"text":"they'd like to draw a smurf, they'd like to draw Micky Mouse."},{"time":30000,"text":"But it turns out to be illegal"},{"time":32000,"text":"to print a child's drawing of Micky Mouse"},{"time":35000,"text":"onto a plate of sugar."},{"time":38000,"text":"And it's a copyright violation."},{"time":40000,"text":"And policing copyright violations"},{"time":42000,"text":"for children's birthday cakes"},{"time":44000,"text":"was such a hassle"},{"time":46000,"text":"that the College Bakery said,"},{"time":48000,"text":"\"You know what, we're getting out of that business."},{"time":50000,"text":"If you're an amateur,"},{"time":52000,"text":"you don't have access to our machine anymore."},{"time":54000,"text":"If you want a printed sugar birthday cake,"},{"time":56000,"text":"you have to use one of our prefab images --"},{"time":60000,"text":"only for professionals.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":62000,"text":"So there's two bills in Congress right now."},{"time":65000,"text":"One is called SOPA, the other is called PIPA."},{"time":67000,"text":"SOPA stands for the Stop Online Piracy Act."},{"time":69000,"text":"It's from the Senate."},{"time":71000,"text":"PIPA is short for PROTECTIP,"},{"time":74000,"text":"which is itself short for"},{"time":76000,"text":"Preventing Real Online Threats"},{"time":78000,"text":"to Economic Creativity"},{"time":80000,"text":"and Theft of Intellectual Property --"},{"time":82000,"text":"because the congressional aides who name these things"},{"time":84000,"text":"have a lot of time on their hands."},{"time":86000,"text":"And what SOPA and PIPA want to do"},{"time":88000,"text":"is they want to do this."},{"time":90000,"text":"They want to raise the cost"},{"time":92000,"text":"of copyright compliance"},{"time":95000,"text":"to the point where people simply get out of the business"},{"time":98000,"text":"of offering it as a capability to amateurs."}]},{"cues":[{"time":101000,"text":"Now the way they propose to do this"},{"time":104000,"text":"is to identify sites"},{"time":106000,"text":"that are substantially infringing on copyright --"},{"time":108000,"text":"although how those sites are identified"},{"time":110000,"text":"is never fully specified in the bills --"},{"time":112000,"text":"and then they want to remove them from the domain name system."},{"time":115000,"text":"They want to take them out of the domain name system."},{"time":117000,"text":"Now the domain name system"},{"time":119000,"text":"is the thing that turns human-readable names, like Google.com,"},{"time":122000,"text":"into the kinds of addresses"},{"time":124000,"text":"machines expect --"},{"time":126000,"text":"74.125.226.212."}]},{"cues":[{"time":131000,"text":"Now the problem with this model of censorship,"},{"time":134000,"text":"of identifying a site"},{"time":136000,"text":"and then trying to remove it from the domain name system,"},{"time":138000,"text":"is that it won't work."},{"time":140000,"text":"And you'd think that would be a pretty big problem for a law,"},{"time":143000,"text":"but Congress seems not to have let that bother them too much."},{"time":145000,"text":"Now the reason it won't work"},{"time":147000,"text":"is that you can still type 74.125.226.212 into the browser"},{"time":151000,"text":"or you can make it a clickable link"},{"time":153000,"text":"and you'll still go to Google."},{"time":156000,"text":"So the policing layer"},{"time":158000,"text":"around the problem"},{"time":160000,"text":"becomes the real threat of the act."}]},{"cues":[{"time":164000,"text":"Now to understand how Congress came to write a bill"},{"time":167000,"text":"that won't accomplish its stated goals,"},{"time":170000,"text":"but will produce a lot of pernicious side effects,"},{"time":172000,"text":"you have to understand a little bit about the back story."},{"time":174000,"text":"And the back story is this:"},{"time":176000,"text":"SOPA and PIPA, as legislation,"},{"time":178000,"text":"were drafted largely by media companies"},{"time":181000,"text":"that were founded in the 20th century."},{"time":183000,"text":"The 20th century was a great time to be a media company,"},{"time":185000,"text":"because the thing you really had on your side was scarcity."},{"time":188000,"text":"If you were making a TV show,"},{"time":190000,"text":"it didn't have to be better than all other TV shows ever made;"},{"time":194000,"text":"it only had to be better"},{"time":196000,"text":"than the two other shows"},{"time":198000,"text":"that were on at the same time --"},{"time":200000,"text":"which is a very low threshold"},{"time":202000,"text":"of competitive difficulty."},{"time":205000,"text":"Which meant"},{"time":207000,"text":"that if you fielded average content,"},{"time":209000,"text":"you got a third of the U.S. public for free --"},{"time":212000,"text":"tens of millions of users"},{"time":215000,"text":"for simply doing something"},{"time":217000,"text":"that wasn't too terrible."},{"time":219000,"text":"This is like having a license to print money"},{"time":221000,"text":"and a barrel of free ink."}]},{"cues":[{"time":223000,"text":"But technology moved on, as technology is wont to do."},{"time":226000,"text":"And slowly, slowly, at the end of the 20th century,"},{"time":229000,"text":"that scarcity started to get eroded --"},{"time":231000,"text":"and I don't mean by digital technology;"},{"time":233000,"text":"I mean by analog technology."},{"time":235000,"text":"Cassette tapes, video cassette recorders,"},{"time":237000,"text":"even the humble Xerox machine"},{"time":239000,"text":"created new opportunities"},{"time":241000,"text":"for us to behave in ways"},{"time":243000,"text":"that astonished the media business."},{"time":245000,"text":"Because it turned out"},{"time":247000,"text":"we're not really couch potatoes."},{"time":249000,"text":"We don't really like to only consume."},{"time":252000,"text":"We do like to consume,"},{"time":254000,"text":"but every time one of these new tools came along,"},{"time":257000,"text":"it turned out we also like to produce"},{"time":259000,"text":"and we like to share."},{"time":261000,"text":"And this freaked the media businesses out --"},{"time":263000,"text":"it freaked them out every time."},{"time":265000,"text":"Jack Valenti, who was the head lobbyist"},{"time":267000,"text":"for the Motion Picture Association of America,"},{"time":269000,"text":"once likened the ferocious video cassette recorder"},{"time":273000,"text":"to Jack the Ripper"},{"time":275000,"text":"and poor, helpless Hollywood"},{"time":277000,"text":"to a woman at home alone."},{"time":280000,"text":"That was the level of rhetoric."}]},{"cues":[{"time":282000,"text":"And so the media industries"},{"time":284000,"text":"begged, insisted, demanded"},{"time":286000,"text":"that Congress do something."},{"time":288000,"text":"And Congress did something."},{"time":290000,"text":"By the early 90s, Congress passed the law"},{"time":292000,"text":"that changed everything."},{"time":295000,"text":"And that law was called the Audio Home Recording Act"},{"time":297000,"text":"of 1992."},{"time":299000,"text":"What the Audio Home Recording Act of 1992 said was,"},{"time":302000,"text":"look, if people are taping stuff off the radio"},{"time":304000,"text":"and then making mixtapes for their friends,"},{"time":307000,"text":"that is not a crime. That's okay."},{"time":310000,"text":"Taping and remixing"},{"time":312000,"text":"and sharing with your friends is okay."},{"time":315000,"text":"If you make lots and lots of high quality copies and you sell them,"},{"time":317000,"text":"that's not okay."},{"time":319000,"text":"But this taping business,"},{"time":321000,"text":"fine, let it go."},{"time":323000,"text":"And they thought that they clarified the issue,"},{"time":326000,"text":"because they'd set out a clear distinction"},{"time":328000,"text":"between legal and illegal copying."}]},{"cues":[{"time":330000,"text":"But that wasn't what the media businesses wanted."},{"time":333000,"text":"They had wanted Congress"},{"time":335000,"text":"to outlaw copying full-stop."},{"time":338000,"text":"So when the Audio Home Recording Act of 1992 was passed,"},{"time":341000,"text":"the media businesses gave up on the idea"},{"time":345000,"text":"of legal versus illegal distinctions for copying"},{"time":347000,"text":"because it was clear"},{"time":349000,"text":"that if Congress was acting in their framework,"},{"time":351000,"text":"they might actually increase the rights of citizens"},{"time":355000,"text":"to participate in our own media environment."},{"time":357000,"text":"So they went for plan B."},{"time":359000,"text":"It took them a while to formulate plan B."}]},{"cues":[{"time":361000,"text":"Plan B appeared in its first full-blown form"},{"time":363000,"text":"in 1998 --"},{"time":365000,"text":"something called the Digital Millennium Copyright Act."},{"time":368000,"text":"It was a complicated piece of legislation, a lot of moving parts."},{"time":370000,"text":"But the main thrust of the DMCA"},{"time":373000,"text":"was that it was legal to sell you"},{"time":375000,"text":"uncopyable digital material --"},{"time":377000,"text":"except that there's no such things as uncopyable digital material."},{"time":380000,"text":"It would be, as Ed Felton once famously said,"},{"time":382000,"text":"\"Like handing out water"},{"time":384000,"text":"that wasn't wet.\""},{"time":386000,"text":"Bits are copyable. That's what computers do."},{"time":389000,"text":"That is a side effect of their ordinary operation."}]},{"cues":[{"time":392000,"text":"So in order to fake the ability"},{"time":394000,"text":"to sell uncopyable bits,"},{"time":396000,"text":"the DMCA also made it legal"},{"time":398000,"text":"to force you to use systems"},{"time":401000,"text":"that broke the copying function of your devices."},{"time":404000,"text":"Every DVD player and game player"},{"time":406000,"text":"and television and computer you brought home --"},{"time":409000,"text":"no matter what you thought you were getting when you bought it --"},{"time":412000,"text":"could be broken by the content industries,"},{"time":415000,"text":"if they wanted to set that as a condition of selling you the content."},{"time":418000,"text":"And to make sure you didn't realize,"},{"time":421000,"text":"or didn't enact their capabilities"},{"time":424000,"text":"as general purpose computing devices,"},{"time":426000,"text":"they also made it illegal"},{"time":428000,"text":"for you to try to reset"},{"time":430000,"text":"the copyability of that content."},{"time":432000,"text":"The DMCA marks the moment"},{"time":434000,"text":"when the media industries"},{"time":436000,"text":"gave up on the legal system"},{"time":438000,"text":"of distinguishing between legal and illegal copying"},{"time":441000,"text":"and simply tried to prevent copying"},{"time":444000,"text":"through technical means."}]},{"cues":[{"time":446000,"text":"Now the DMCA had, and is continuing to have, a lot of complicated effects,"},{"time":449000,"text":"but in this one domain, limiting sharing,"},{"time":452000,"text":"it has mostly not worked."},{"time":454000,"text":"And the main reason it hasn't worked"},{"time":456000,"text":"is the Internet has turned out to be far more popular and far more powerful"},{"time":459000,"text":"than anyone imagined."},{"time":462000,"text":"The mixtape, the fanzine,"},{"time":464000,"text":"that was nothing compared to what we're seeing now"},{"time":466000,"text":"with the Internet."},{"time":468000,"text":"We are in a world"},{"time":470000,"text":"where most American citizens"},{"time":472000,"text":"over the age of 12"},{"time":474000,"text":"share things with each other online."},{"time":476000,"text":"We share written things, we share images,"},{"time":478000,"text":"we share audio, we share video."},{"time":480000,"text":"Some of the stuff we share is stuff we've made."},{"time":482000,"text":"Some of the stuff we share is stuff we've found."},{"time":484000,"text":"Some of the stuff we share"},{"time":486000,"text":"is stuff we've made out of what we've found,"},{"time":488000,"text":"and all of it horrifies those industries."}]},{"cues":[{"time":491000,"text":"So PIPA and SOPA"},{"time":493000,"text":"are round two."},{"time":495000,"text":"But where the DMCA was surgical --"},{"time":497000,"text":"we want to go down into your computer,"},{"time":500000,"text":"we want to go down into your television set, down into your game machine,"},{"time":503000,"text":"and prevent it from doing"},{"time":505000,"text":"what they said it would do at the store --"},{"time":507000,"text":"PIPA and SOPA are nuclear"},{"time":509000,"text":"and they're saying, we want to go anywhere in the world"},{"time":513000,"text":"and censor content."},{"time":515000,"text":"Now the mechanism, as I said, for doing this,"},{"time":518000,"text":"is you need to take out anybody"},{"time":521000,"text":"pointing to those IP addresses."},{"time":523000,"text":"You need to take them out of search engines,"},{"time":525000,"text":"you need to take them out of online directories,"},{"time":527000,"text":"you need to take them out of user lists."},{"time":530000,"text":"And because the biggest producers of content on the Internet"},{"time":534000,"text":"are not Google and Yahoo,"},{"time":537000,"text":"they're us,"},{"time":539000,"text":"we're the people getting policed."},{"time":541000,"text":"Because in the end,"},{"time":543000,"text":"the real threat"},{"time":546000,"text":"to the enactment of PIPA and SOPA"},{"time":549000,"text":"is our ability to share things with one another."}]},{"cues":[{"time":552000,"text":"So what PIPA and SOPA risk doing"},{"time":555000,"text":"is taking a centuries-old legal concept,"},{"time":558000,"text":"innocent until proven guilty,"},{"time":560000,"text":"and reversing it --"},{"time":562000,"text":"guilty until proven innocent."},{"time":564000,"text":"You can't share"},{"time":566000,"text":"until you show us"},{"time":569000,"text":"that you're not sharing something"},{"time":571000,"text":"we don't like."},{"time":573000,"text":"Suddenly, the burden of proof for legal versus illegal"},{"time":576000,"text":"falls affirmatively on us"},{"time":578000,"text":"and on the services"},{"time":580000,"text":"that might be offering us any new capabilities."},{"time":583000,"text":"And if it costs even a dime"},{"time":586000,"text":"to police a user,"},{"time":588000,"text":"that will crush a service"},{"time":590000,"text":"with a hundred million users."}]},{"cues":[{"time":592000,"text":"So this is the Internet they have in mind."},{"time":594000,"text":"Imagine this sign everywhere --"},{"time":597000,"text":"except imagine it doesn't say College Bakery,"},{"time":600000,"text":"imagine it says YouTube"},{"time":602000,"text":"and Facebook and Twitter."},{"time":604000,"text":"Imagine it says TED,"},{"time":606000,"text":"because the comments can't be policed"},{"time":609000,"text":"at any acceptable cost."},{"time":612000,"text":"The real effects of SOPA and PIPA"},{"time":615000,"text":"are going to be different than the proposed effects."},{"time":618000,"text":"The threat, in fact,"},{"time":620000,"text":"is this inversion of the burden of proof,"},{"time":623000,"text":"where we suddenly"},{"time":625000,"text":"are all treated like thieves"},{"time":627000,"text":"at every moment we're given the freedom to create,"},{"time":630000,"text":"to produce or to share."},{"time":633000,"text":"And the people who provide those capabilities to us --"},{"time":636000,"text":"the YouTubes, the Facebooks, the Twitters and TEDs --"},{"time":639000,"text":"are in the business"},{"time":641000,"text":"of having to police us,"},{"time":643000,"text":"or being on the hook for contributory infringement."}]},{"cues":[{"time":646000,"text":"There's two things you can do"},{"time":648000,"text":"to help stop this --"},{"time":650000,"text":"a simple thing and a complicated thing,"},{"time":653000,"text":"an easy thing and a hard thing."},{"time":655000,"text":"The simple thing, the easy thing, is this:"},{"time":657000,"text":"if you're an American citizen,"},{"time":659000,"text":"call your representative, call your senator."},{"time":662000,"text":"When you look at"},{"time":665000,"text":"the people who co-signed on the SOPA bill,"},{"time":668000,"text":"people who've co-signed on PIPA,"},{"time":670000,"text":"what you see is that they have cumulatively received"},{"time":673000,"text":"millions and millions of dollars"},{"time":676000,"text":"from the traditional media industries."},{"time":678000,"text":"You don't have millions and millions of dollars,"},{"time":680000,"text":"but you can call your representatives,"},{"time":682000,"text":"and you can remind them that you vote,"},{"time":685000,"text":"and you can ask not to be treated like a thief,"},{"time":688000,"text":"and you can suggest that you would prefer"},{"time":690000,"text":"that the Internet not be broken."}]},{"cues":[{"time":693000,"text":"And if you're not an American citizen,"},{"time":695000,"text":"you can contact American citizens that you know"},{"time":697000,"text":"and encourage them to do the same."},{"time":699000,"text":"Because this seems like a national issue,"},{"time":701000,"text":"but it is not."},{"time":703000,"text":"These industries will not be content"},{"time":705000,"text":"with breaking our Internet."},{"time":707000,"text":"If they break it, they will break it for everybody."},{"time":710000,"text":"That's the easy thing."},{"time":712000,"text":"That's the simple thing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":714000,"text":"The hard thing is this:"},{"time":716000,"text":"get ready, because more is coming."},{"time":719000,"text":"SOPA is simply a reversion of COICA,"},{"time":722000,"text":"which was purposed last year, which did not pass."},{"time":724000,"text":"And all of this goes back"},{"time":726000,"text":"to the failure of the DMCA"},{"time":728000,"text":"to disallow sharing as a technical means."},{"time":730000,"text":"And the DMCA goes back to the Audio Home Recording Act,"},{"time":733000,"text":"which horrified those industries."},{"time":735000,"text":"Because the whole business"},{"time":737000,"text":"of actually suggesting that someone is breaking the law"},{"time":740000,"text":"and then gathering evidence and proving that,"},{"time":742000,"text":"that turns out to be really inconvenient."},{"time":745000,"text":"\"We'd prefer not to do that,\""},{"time":747000,"text":"says the content industries."},{"time":749000,"text":"And what they want is not to have to do that."},{"time":752000,"text":"They don't want legal distinctions"},{"time":754000,"text":"between legal and illegal sharing."},{"time":756000,"text":"They just want the sharing to go away."}]},{"cues":[{"time":758000,"text":"PIPA and SOPA are not oddities, they're not anomalies,"},{"time":761000,"text":"they're not events."},{"time":763000,"text":"They're the next turn of this particular screw,"},{"time":766000,"text":"which has been going on 20 years now."},{"time":768000,"text":"And if we defeat these, as I hope we do,"},{"time":770000,"text":"more is coming."},{"time":772000,"text":"Because until we convince Congress"},{"time":777000,"text":"that the way to deal with copyright violation"},{"time":780000,"text":"is the way copyright violation was dealt with with Napster, with YouTube,"},{"time":784000,"text":"which is to have a trial with all the presentation of evidence"},{"time":787000,"text":"and the hashing out of facts and the assessment of remedies"},{"time":790000,"text":"that goes on in democratic societies."},{"time":792000,"text":"That's the way to handle this."}]},{"cues":[{"time":794000,"text":"In the meantime,"},{"time":796000,"text":"the hard thing to do is to be ready."},{"time":798000,"text":"Because that's the real message of PIPA and SOPA."},{"time":800000,"text":"Time Warner has called"},{"time":802000,"text":"and they want us all back on the couch,"},{"time":804000,"text":"just consuming --"},{"time":806000,"text":"not producing, not sharing --"},{"time":808000,"text":"and we should say, \"No.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":810000,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":812000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}